arts.ttl: Just in: Barcelona midfielder leaves Spain training with injury; doubt vs Georgia
arts.sum: Problems continue to mount for FC Barcelona with regard to injuries as one of their first-team stars seem to have picked up a fresh problem while on national team duty.
